@page
@model Web_shop.Pages.FaqModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Često postavljena pitanja";
    Layout = "_Layout";
}
<header class="p-3 bg-dark text-white">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="d-flex flex-wrap align-items-center justify-content-center justify-content-lg-start">
            <a href="/">
                <img src="~/Images/logo.png" alt="Logo" style="width: 100px;" />
            </a>

            <ul class="nav col-12 col-lg-auto me-lg-auto mb-2 justify-content-center mb-md-0">
                <li><a href="/" class="nav-link px-2 text-white">Početna stranica</a></li>
                <li><a href="/Category" class="nav-link px-2 text-white">Kategorije</a></li>
                <li><a href="/Delivery" class="nav-link px-2 text-white">Dostava i plaćanje</a></li>
                <li><a href="/Faq" class="nav-link px-2 text-secondary">Česta pitanja</a></li>
                <li><a href="/About" class="nav-link px-2 text-white">O nama</a></li>
            </ul>

            <form class="col-12 col-lg-auto mb-3 mb-lg-0 me-lg-3">
                <input type="search" id="searchInput" class="form-control form-control-light" placeholder="Traži..." aria-label="Tražilica">
            </form>

            <div class="text-end">
                @if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(Model.Username))
                {
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-light me-2" onclick="window.location.href = '/Account/Login'">Prijava</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-warning" onclick="window.location.href = '/Account/Register'">Registracija</button>
                }
                else
                {
                    <div class="dropdown-center">
                        <button id="profileButton" class="btn btn-secondary dropdown-toggle" type="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false" style="font-size: x-large;">
                            👤
                        </button>
                        <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/ShoppingCart">🛒 Košarica</a></li>
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/Account/Logout">Odjava</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                }
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>
<br />
<h1 class="text-center text-secondary">Često postavljena pitanja</h1>
<br />

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="accordion w-100" id="basicAccordion">
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                        data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#basicAccordionCollapseOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                    Kako mogu naručiti proizvode?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="basicAccordionCollapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingOne"
                 data-bs-parent="#basicAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    <strong>Naručivanje proizvoda je jednostavno!</strong> Prijavite se na svoj račun, odaberite proizvode koje želite kupiti, dodajte ih u košaricu i slijedite upute za plaćanje.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                        data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#basicAccordionCollapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                    Koje načine plaćanja prihvaćate?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="basicAccordionCollapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo"
                 data-bs-parent="#basicAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    <strong>Plaćanje je fleksibilno i sigurno.</strong> Prihvaćamo kreditne kartice (Visa, MasterCard, American Express), PayPal, te plaćanje pouzećem.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                        data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#basicAccordionCollapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                    Koliko traje dostava?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="basicAccordionCollapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree"
                 data-bs-parent="#basicAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    <strong>Dostava je brza i pouzdana.</strong> Rok isporuke je obično 1-3 radna dana, ovisno o lokaciji i dostupnosti proizvoda.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                        data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#basicAccordionCollapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                    Kako mogu pratiti svoju narudžbu?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="basicAccordionCollapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour"
                 data-bs-parent="#basicAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    <strong>Pratite svoju narudžbu u nekoliko jednostavnih koraka.</strong> Nakon što je vaša narudžba poslana, dobit ćete email s informacijama za praćenje. Također možete pratiti status svoje narudžbe prijavom na svoj račun na našoj web stranici.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFive">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                        data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#basicAccordionCollapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
                    Koja je politika povrata proizvoda?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="basicAccordionCollapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive"
                 data-bs-parent="#basicAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    <strong>Vaše zadovoljstvo nam je važno.</strong> Ako niste zadovoljni kupljenim proizvodom, možete ga vratiti unutar 14 dana od primitka. Proizvod mora biti neotvoren i u originalnom pakiranju. Kontaktirajte našu službu za korisnike za više informacija o procesu povrata.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="fixed-bottom">
    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <footer class="py-3 my-4">
        <p class="text-center text-body-secondary">© 2024 DućanPlus, d.o.o.</p>
    </footer>
</div>
